title: Beginner Level English - Foundations
details: The Complete English Language Course: English grammar, English speaking, and writing. British and American English.At the beginning of each lecture, we learn useful vocabulary. We will then see how to use this vocabulary in realistic, practical ways. After that, we will look at an example dialogue, which shows how two native speakers might casually discuss the topic in question. In addition to the vocabulary and sentence structures, I will also teach you three idioms in each video. Idioms are important phrases used by native speakers in order to speak more casually and expressively. To review, there will be a fill in the blanks exercise and a speaking assignment. This is the basic structure of each video in this course.
